Class ConstraintBlockerTermStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.reasoner.term.blocker.ConstraintBlockerTermStore

    Iterable<ConstraintBlockerTerm>, TermStore<ConstraintBlockerTerm>

    public class ConstraintBlockerTermStore
extends Object
implements TermStore<ConstraintBlockerTerm>
    A TermStore to hold blocks. See ConstraintBlockerTermGenerator for details on the constraint blocking process.
